from itertools import permutations

collage = np.zeros((n * 3, n * 2, 3), dtype=lena.dtype)

for k, prm in enumerate(permutations(range(3))):
    x, y = k // 2, k % 2
    collage[n * x : n * (x + 1), n * y : n * (y + 1)] = lena[:, :, prm]
    
plt.imshow(collage)

M = np.array([
    [0.412453, 0.357580, 0.180423],
    [0.212671, 0.715160, 0.072169],
    [0.019334, 0.119193, 0.950227]
])

cst1 = 0.008856

g = lambda t: ((t + 0.055) / 1.055) ** 2.4 * 100 if t > 0.04045 else t / 12.92 * 100
f = lambda t: t**(1/3) if t > cst1 else (903.3 * t + 16) / 116

lena_lab_my = lena.copy().astype(np.float64) / 255

for i in range(n):
    for j in range(n):
        for k in range(3):
            lena_lab_my[i, j, k] = g(lena_lab_my[i, j, k])

lena_lab_my = np.array([[np.matmul(M, lena_lab_my[i, j]) for j in range(n)] for i in range(n)])

lena_lab_my[:,:,0] /= 95.047
lena_lab_my[:,:,1] /= 100
lena_lab_my[:,:,2] /= 108.883

lena_xyz = lena_lab_my.copy()

lena_lab_my[:,:,0] = [[max(116 * f(lena_xyz[i, j, 1]) - 16, 0) for j in range(n)] for i in range(n)]

lena_lab_my[:,:,1] = [[500 * (f(lena_xyz[i, j, 0]) - f(lena_xyz[i, j, 1])) for j in range(n)]
                      for i in range(n)]

lena_lab_my[:,:,2] = [[200 * (f(lena_xyz[i, j, 1]) - f(lena_xyz[i, j, 2])) for j in range(n)]
                      for i in range(n)]
            
lena_lab_my[:,:,0] *= 255 / 100
lena_lab_my[:,:,1:] += 128
